note: Good Dog. Often skeptical. Occasionally sniffing where I shouldn’t. Always happy to see you. Happily living in the far north of Minnesota, watching a bit of hockey or football “SKOL,” hiking around, or I’ll just hop in the boat and hope someone will take me somewhere…. Ope! I enjoy being curious about everything. As a private individual, I also know connection with others in meaningful ways is what it’s all about. Be safe and be kind.
